freesmartphone.org Framework DBus Interface Specification

org.freesmartphone.PIM.Sources

Description

This interface gives access to PIM Sources.

Namespace

org.freesmartphone.PIM.Sources

Methods

  • InitAllEntries
  • GetEntryCount
  • GetDomains
  • GetDefaultBackend
  • GetBackends

Signals

None

Errors

None

Methods

InitAllEntries ( )

Description: Initialize all backend sources.

GetEntryCount ( ) → i

Description: Get the number of sources available.

Returns

i: count

Amount of sources.

GetDomains ( ) → as

Description: Get the list of PIM domains.

Returns

as: domains

List of available PIM domains.

GetDefaultBackend ( s ) → s

Description: Get the default backend for specified domain.

Parameters

s: domain

Name of domain.

Returns

s: backend

Name of default backend for given domain.

GetBackends ( ) → as

Description: Get list of available backends.

Returns

as: backends

List of backends.
